WITH EventsWithTriJet AS (
 SELECT *, (
  SELECT ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M3(j1, j2, j3) AS j123
       FROM (SELECT (j).* FROM UNNEST(Jet) WITH ORDINALITY as j) AS j1,
            (SELECT (j).* FROM UNNEST(Jet) WITH ORDINALITY as j) AS j2,
            (SELECT (j).* FROM UNNEST(Jet) WITH ORDINALITY as j) AS j3
       WHERE j1.ordinality < j2.ordinality AND j2.ordinality < j3.ordinality
       ORDER BY ABS((ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M3(j1, j2, j3)).mass - $1) ASC LIMIT $2) AS triJet
 FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_128000
)
SELECT HISTOGRAM_BIN((e.triJet).pt, $3, $4, ($5 - $6) / $7) AS x,
  COUNT(*) AS y
FROM EventsWithTriJet AS e
WHERE triJet IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

  SELECT (
    SELECT array_agg(j)

  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_8192000 AS e
)

  ($8 - $9) / $10) AS x, COUNT(*) AS y
FROM GoodJets AS Jets
WHERE array_length(Jets.Jet, $11) > $12
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

WITH EventsWithLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, 
    array_cat(
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $1) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Muon) as x),
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $2) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Electron) as x)) AS Lepton
  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_32000 AS e
), EventsWithTriLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, l1, l2, 
      (SELECT CAST(ROW(l3.pt, l3.eta, l3.phi, l3.mass, l3.charge, $3) AS leptonType)
        FROM UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l3(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
        WHERE 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l1.idx AND 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l2.idx
        ORDER BY l3.pt DESC
        LIMIT $4) AS l3
  FROM EventsWithLeptons AS e
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l1(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l2(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  WHERE
    ARRAY_LENGTH(e.Lepton, $5) > $6 AND
    l1.idx < l2.idx AND
    l1.charge != l2.charge AND
    l1.type = l2.type
), EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked AS (
  SELECT MET, l3, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY event ORDER BY ABS($7 - (ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M2(l1, l2)).mass)) r 
  FROM EventsWithTriLeptons
)
SELECT HISTOGRAM_BIN(SQRT($8 * (e.MET).pt * (e.l3).pt * ($9 - 
  COS(DELTA_PHI((e.MET).phi, (e.l3).phi)))), $10, $11, ($12 - $13) / 
  $14) AS x, COUNT(*) AS y
FROM EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked as e
WHERE e.r = $15
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_16384000 AS e
WHERE EXISTS(
  SELECT *
  FROM (SELECT (m).* FROM UNNEST(Muon) WITH ORDINALITY AS m) AS m1,
       (SELECT (m).* FROM UNNEST(Muon) WITH ORDINALITY AS m) AS m2
  WHERE
    m1.ordinality < m2.ordinality AND
    m1.charge != m2.charge AND
    INVARIANT_MASS(m1, m2) BETWEEN $6 AND $7)
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

        COUNT(*) AS y
FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_65536000 CROSS JOIN UNNEST(Jet) as j
WHERE ABS((j).eta) < $6
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

  WHERE

WITH EventsWithLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, 
    array_cat(
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $1) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Muon) as x),
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $2) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Electron) as x)) AS Lepton
  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_16384000 AS e
), EventsWithTriLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, l1, l2, 
      (SELECT CAST(ROW(l3.pt, l3.eta, l3.phi, l3.mass, l3.charge, $3) AS leptonType)
        FROM UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l3(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
        WHERE 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l1.idx AND 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l2.idx
        ORDER BY l3.pt DESC
        LIMIT $4) AS l3
  FROM EventsWithLeptons AS e
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l1(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l2(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  WHERE
    ARRAY_LENGTH(e.Lepton, $5) > $6 AND
    l1.idx < l2.idx AND
    l1.charge != l2.charge AND
    l1.type = l2.type
), EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked AS (
  SELECT MET, l3, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY event ORDER BY ABS($7 - (ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M2(l1, l2)).mass)) r 
  FROM EventsWithTriLeptons
)
SELECT HISTOGRAM_BIN(SQRT($8 * (e.MET).pt * (e.l3).pt * ($9 - 
  COS(DELTA_PHI((e.MET).phi, (e.l3).phi)))), $10, $11, ($12 - $13) / 
  $14) AS x, COUNT(*) AS y
FROM EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked as e
WHERE e.r = $15
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

WITH EventsWithTriJet AS (

  SELECT ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M3(j1, j2, j3) AS j123
       FROM (SELECT (j).* FROM UNNEST(Jet) WITH ORDINALITY as j) AS j1,

       ORDER BY ABS((ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M3(j1, j2, j3)).mass - $1) ASC LIMIT $2) AS triJet

GROUP BY x

WITH EventsWithLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, 
    array_cat(
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $1) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Muon) as x),
      (SELECT array_agg(CAST(ROW(x.pt, x.eta, x.phi, x.mass, x.charge, $2) AS leptonType)) FROM UNNEST(e.Electron) as x)) AS Lepton
  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_4096000 AS e
), EventsWithTriLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, l1, l2, 
      (SELECT CAST(ROW(l3.pt, l3.eta, l3.phi, l3.mass, l3.charge, $3) AS leptonType)
        FROM UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l3(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
        WHERE 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l1.idx AND 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l2.idx
        ORDER BY l3.pt DESC
        LIMIT $4) AS l3
  FROM EventsWithLeptons AS e
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l1(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l2(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  WHERE
    ARRAY_LENGTH(e.Lepton, $5) > $6 AND
    l1.idx < l2.idx AND
    l1.charge != l2.charge AND
    l1.type = l2.type
), EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked AS (
  SELECT MET, l3, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY event ORDER BY ABS($7 - (ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M2(l1, l2)).mass)) r 
  FROM EventsWithTriLeptons
)
SELECT HISTOGRAM_BIN(SQRT($8 * (e.MET).pt * (e.l3).pt * ($9 - 
  COS(DELTA_PHI((e.MET).phi, (e.l3).phi)))), $10, $11, ($12 - $13) / 
  $14) AS x, COUNT(*) AS y
FROM EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked as e
WHERE e.r = $15
GROUP BY x
ORDER BY x

  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_256000 AS e
), EventsWithTriLeptons AS (
  SELECT e.*, l1, l2, 
      (SELECT CAST(ROW(l3.pt, l3.eta, l3.phi, l3.mass, l3.charge, $3) AS leptonType)
        FROM UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l3(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
        WHERE 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l1.idx AND 
        CAST(l3.idx AS int) != l2.idx
        ORDER BY l3.pt DESC
        LIMIT $4) AS l3
  FROM EventsWithLeptons AS e
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l1(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)
  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(e.Lepton) WITH ORDINALITY AS l2(pt, eta, phi, mass, charge, type, idx)

    l1.charge != l2.charge AND
    l1.type = l2.type
), EventsWithTriLeptonsRanked AS (
  SELECT MET, l3, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY event ORDER BY ABS($7 - (ADD_PT_ETA_PHI_M2(l1, l2)).mass)) r 
  FROM EventsWithTriLeptons
)
SELECT HISTOGRAM_BIN(SQRT($8 * (e.MET).pt * (e.l3).pt * ($9 - 
  COS(DELTA_PHI((e.MET).phi, (e.l3).phi)))), $10, $11, ($12 - $13) / 
  $14) AS x, COUNT(*) AS y

      j.pt > $1 AND
      NOT EXISTS (SELECT p FROM UNNEST(e.Muon) AS p
                  WHERE p.pt > $2 AND DELTA_R(p.eta, p.phi, j.eta, j.phi) < $3) AND
      NOT EXISTS (SELECT p FROM UNNEST(e.Electron) AS p
                  WHERE p.pt > $4 AND DELTA_R(p.eta, p.phi, j.eta, j.phi) < $5)) AS Jet
  FROM Run2012B_SingleMu_128000 AS e
)

GROUP BY x
